required_parameters.name: regionId
required_parameters.description:

optional_parameters.name: priceReduced
optional_parameters.description:
Price reduced
Ex: `1-`
Choose one of the values below
`1-`: Less than 1 day
`3-`: Less than 3 days
`7-`: Less than 7 days
`14-`: Less than 14 days
`30-`: Less than 30 days
`-30`: More than 30 days
`-60`: More than 60 days
`-120`: More than 120 days
`-`: Any time

optional_parameters.name: page
optional_parameters.description:
The page index, for paging purpose
Ex: `2`
Default value: `1`

optional_parameters.name: hoaFees
optional_parameters.description:
HOA fees
Ex: `0`
Choose one of the values below
`0`: No Hoa
`25`: $25/month
`50`: $50/month
`75`: $75/month
...............

optional_parameters.name: greatSchoolsRating
optional_parameters.description:
GreatSchools rating
Ex: `1`
Choose one of the values below
`1`: 1+
`2`: 2+
........
`10`: 10

optional_parameters.description:

Ex: `250`
Choose one of the values below
`250`: $250/year
`500`: $500/year
`750`: $750/year
`1000`: $1000/year
...............

optional_parameters.name: priceSqft
optional_parameters.description:
Price/Sq. Ft.
Min and max price/Sq. Ft should be separated by commas

In the case of only having the minimum price/Sq. Ft: Ex: `100`
In the case of only having the maximum price/Sq. Ft: Ex: `,250`
In case of having both: Ex: `100,250`

`100`: 100
`150`: 150
`200`: 200
............
